project  : NEST 3 DEEP — a nested-lattice visualization (three.js / WebGL)
honesty  : a VISUALIZATION, not an emergent system and not a mind. Three nested 10×10×10
           wireframe lattices with a photon walking a base-1000 odometer toward "infinity."
           The motion is deterministic and scripted — idx=(idx+1)%1000 with carry — with no
           coupling, no synchronization, no basin, no noise, and nothing measured. The
           "observers" pulse on sin(time). NO ACI is minted: there is no emergence here, only
           beautiful clockwork. Emergence must be measured before it earns a face (see tetraktys).
